sequenceDiagram
    participant Mobile as Mobile App
    participant Main as Main Service
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant RAG as RAG Service
    participant Chroma as ChromaDB
    participant Mongo as MongoDB

    Mobile->>Main: POST /chat/messages/stream
    Main->>PG: Tạo hoặc lấy hội thoại
    Main->>PG: Lưu tin nhắn người dùng
    Main-->>Mobile: event ready
    Main->>RAG: POST /rag/agent-search/stream
    RAG-->>Main: progress validate, analyze
    Main-->>Mobile: event progress
    RAG->>Chroma: Truy hồi vector chunks
    RAG->>Mongo: Đối chiếu metadata nguồn
    RAG-->>Main: progress retrieve, synthesize, verify
    Main-->>Mobile: event progress
    RAG-->>Main: done answer, sources
    Main->>PG: Lưu tin nhắn trả lời
    Main-->>Mobile: event done
    Mobile->>Main: GET suggested-questions
    Main-->>Mobile: suggested_questions
